  - Externally-authored essays referenced by analysis. The worked-
    examples collection includes Frame Check analyses of two externally-
    authored documents whose text is NOT bundled (referenced via
    source_document_url metadata only):
    - The Federal Reserve March 2026 FOMC Statement (federalreserve.gov)
      analyzed in data/worked_examples/fomc-statement-march-2026.md
    - "The Intelligence Age" (Sam Altman, 2024, ia.samaltman.com)
      analyzed in data/worked_examples/the-intelligence-age-altman-2024.md
